data.description: WOW!  LOOK AT THIS REDUCTION! Incredible midcentury-modern home offers a terrific layout, inside & out, for entertaining & enjoying the outdoors!  Large, 1/2+ acre corner lot offers a double carport w/storage room, private backyard w/workshop and another storage room, open patio, and a screened porch.  Interior layout features a den-style living room w/fireplace, country kitchen/dining combo, large bonus room, huge master suite w/walk-in closet, powder area w/dual sinks & tub/shower combo, and 2 more cozy bedrooms w/a shared full bathroom.  Updated are needed; but there is also plenty of original, quality features that really make this mid-mod stand out!  EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY.
